    "These lengths exceed the maximum generation capacity of proprietary models, which is limited to around 4,096 tokens.",
    "Among the baselines, Mixtral produces the longest generations, averaging over 1,500 tokens, while Mistral-Instruct generates the shortest outputs, around 1,100 tokens per generation.",
    "9 Measured using tiktoken package (https://github.",
    "com/openai/tiktoken) with \"o200k_base\" encoding.",
    "10 Experiment done using greedy decoding, max_token=10K."
